This section introduces the Software Requirements Specification (SRS) for the Predictive Stock Management System.

Purpose

The purpose of this document is to clearly define system requirements for developers, testers, and stakeholders.

Scope

The system manages inventory data and predicts future stock requirements to help businesses plan better.

Definitions & Acronyms

SRS – Software Requirements Specification

Admin – User managing system access

Prediction – Estimated future stock demand

Inventory – Stored goods and products

This introduction provides a clear understanding of the system before detailing requirements.
